thread.title: Paul Wynne

author: Paul Wynne
title: Paul Wynne
text:
The tap and hose connectors are seriously over engineered compared to the competition!
I was initially reluctant to buy on line as I like to physically see and handle products before buying them. However, after continually buying poor quality fittings from the usual DIY outlets I took a 'risk' and bought on line. I only wish I had done it sooner. No regrets and no problems. Good communication with regards to the delivery date. Thank you.
